{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_01_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 トリエルを見学",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.033333420753479004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ予選が差し迫ったある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day‚ before the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix\nqualifying round",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.5333333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800,
          "startTime": 5.333333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あ。おはようございます。星見プロの\n{user}さん、やったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ good morning. You’re\n{user}-san of Hoshimi Productions‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEの鈴村優いいます\n今日は一日よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Yu Suzumura of TRINITYAiLE.\nMuch obliged for bein’ here today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそよろしくお願いします。今日はレッスンを\n見学させてもらえるとのことで、お邪魔しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ thank you for your time. For\nletting me visit the lesson today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん達のレッスンからは\n得るものが沢山あると思うので、楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m looking forward to your lesson.\nI’m sure I’ll learn a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "得るものやなんてそんなん……\nこれはうちらも張り切らないとやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There ain’t so much to learn…\nLooks like we’ll have to do our best then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんはうちの子達にとっても憧れですから\n今日も見学だと言ったら、連れて行けってうるさくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our girls all admire you three.\nWhen I said I was going to visit‚ they were hassling me to take them along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ、普段は見学を一切拒否してるんで\nなかなか難しいかもしれませんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yea? Well‚ we usually refuse all visits‚\nso this might be rare for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうと、まだレッスンには早いですから\n待ってもらうことになるけど、よろしいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ it’s still early for the lesson‚\nso you’ll have to wait. Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大丈夫です\n……ところで、それは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nBy the way‚ what’s that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、これですか？\nご覧の通り、掃除道具です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean this?\nAs you can see‚ it’s cleaning equipment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンが始まる前に\nレッスン室を掃除しておこう思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before the lesson starts‚\nI thought I’d clean the room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "掃除……鈴村さんがですか？\nわざわざ自分でやらなくても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cleaning… You’d do it yourself‚ Suzumura-san?\nEven if you don’t go to the hassle of doing it yourself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、スタジオにも清掃の方はいてはります\nでも、清掃の時間はいつも決まってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ the studio has a cleaner too.\nBut the cleaning times are always fixed‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "このスタジオにはいつもお世話になってますし\nそれぐらいはしときたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and this studio has always used by us‚\nso I want to do this much for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんが気持ち良く\n練習出来るようにって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also I want Rui-chan and Sumire-chan to feel good while\nrehearsing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、うちは掃除をするんで\nもう少し待ってもらえます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I’ll clean up.\nPlease wait a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "一人じゃ大変でしょう。俺も手伝います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a lot to do on your own. I’ll help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "お気遣いありがとうございます\nでも、ここはうち一人で十分ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for asking.\nBut I can take care of this by myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはお客様やん？\nレッスンが始まるまで、ゆっくりしてて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a guest‚ {user}-san.\nSo please take it easy until the lesson starts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、雑巾がけは俺に任せて下さい\nささっと終わらせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ please‚ leave the wiping to me.\nI’ll finish it in no time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "くふっ、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3899.9999999999914,
          "startTime": 127.83333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "――ふうっ\n鈴村さん、これで終わりでいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew.\nIs this good enough‚ Suzumura-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで\nいつもより、はよ終わりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ {user}-san‚\nI’ve finished earlier than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "紅茶を淹れたんで\nもし良かったら飲んでください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made some black tea.\nWould you like some?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "おっ、ありがとうございます。それじゃあ、遠慮なく\n凄く美味しいですね。なんて種類の紅茶なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ I would like some.\nThis is delicious. What kind of tea is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "今日はウバを淹れてみました\nお口に合って良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today I tried Uva.\nI’m glad you like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そろそろ瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんが\n来る頃やわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Rui-chan and Sumire-chan should\nbe here soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんと奥山さんか……\nやっぱりうちの子達にも見せてやりたかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san and Okuyama-san…\nA shame I couldn’t show this to our girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみなさんがそんなん思ってくれてはるなんて\n感激ですわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m impressed that the members at Hoshimi Productions\nthink that much of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "そうやなぁ……良ければ今度、そちらのレッスンを\n見学させていただけませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see. In that case‚ could we visit one of your\nlessons next time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "うちらを慕ってくれはる子達と\nもっと仲良うなりたいって思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I’d like to get a lot closer to\ngirls who like us so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、今後うちらを脅かすかもしれない\n後輩達の実力を見ておきたいですから……ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ they might be threats to us in future.\nSo I’d like to see how good our juniors are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "脅かす存在……か。その言葉、聞いたら喜ぶだろうな\nあ、代わりにうちの子達にも見学させてもらうのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A threat? They’ll be happy to hear that you said so.\nSo in return‚ you’ll let our girls visit here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "それは\n{user}さんのお役目やん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that\nyour role‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達の代わりに\nうちらのレッスンを見学するんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll be watching our lesson\nin their place‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_01-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、それ以上は禁止です\nそれでよろしいですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but more than that is prohibited.\nAre you okay with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
